data.description: Nestled in the charming town of Ragley, this inviting property boasts a blend  of modern comforts and timeless appeal. With three bedrooms and two bathrooms,  this home offers ample space for both relaxation and entertainment. Boasting a  young age of just 3.5 years, it exudes a fresh ambiance. Recent enhancements  include the addition of a sleek electric fireplace, meticulously crafted  landscaping, and an expansive concrete back patio, perfect for hosting  gatherings or enjoying serene outdoor moments. Step inside to discover newly  installed flooring throughout the bedrooms, adding a touch of elegance and  warmth. Situated on a generous 0.45 acre lot, there's plenty of room to roam  and unwind. Additionally, its location in Flood Zone X, where flood insurance  is not typically required. Whether you're seeking a peaceful retreat or a place  to call home, this property offers both comfort and convenience in a  picturesque setting.
